{"word":"G2694 - κατασύρω - katasýrō - kat-as-oo'-ro - Hale","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατασύρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katasýrō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-as-oo'-ro</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hale</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொண்டுபோ"},{"paragraph":"1. to draw down, pull down"},{"paragraph":"2. to draw along, drag forcibly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G4951 - σύρω - sýrō - soo'-ro/4951\">G4951</a>; to <i>drag down</i>, that is, <i>arrest</i> judicially: - hale.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}